Package: shadowtext
Title: Shadow Text Grob and Layer
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Guangchuang", "Yu", email = "guangchuangyu@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implement shadowtextGrob() for 'grid' and geom_shadowtext() layer for 'ggplot2'.
